{"tid":1179143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要請廣傳］各位反送中聯署發起人，咪參加林輝或任何要你留telegram既’後續行動‘","createTime":"2019-05-31T02:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T15:28:55.000Z","uid":48083,"like":67,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"42d3b1854269525ecf9bc4614f3e7c081078d5c5","tid":1179143,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:00:59.000Z","msg":"事緣：<br />\n<br />\n林輝 呢條友被抨擊係左膠，呢個大家都知。⋯⋯，依家佢條友公開要搵各校聯署嘅召集人，話有嘢進一步商討，我就決定面都費時俾爆樽。你條友想幫沈旭暉同佢後台老闆葉國華搜集情報，呢啲關鍵時候仲幫共產黨做嘢。大佬，你條友做人仲有無底線可言，大家可以直接ignore佢，有乜事6月9日港島見。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0yganT2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0yganT2.png&h=547c32d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯你條友係唔係想搞膠個運動，焦土派變咗廢人就出左膠部隊，我十分之聞到呢陣除<br />\n你條友同沈旭暉有密切關係，你想俾情報葉國華，有樣嘢，我係十分之贊同香港土共史專家梁慕嫻，就係葉國華絕對係一件仆街。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://martinoei.com/article/27056/%e6%9e%97%e8%bc%9d-%e6%94%b6%e5%92%97%e6%9f%af%e6%89%93%e5%b9%ab%e6%b2%88%e6%97%ad%e6%9a%89%e6%90%9c%e9%9b%86%e6%83%85%e5%a0%b1%ef%bc%9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmartinoei.com%2Farticle%2F27056%2F%25e6%259e%2597%25e8%25bc%259d-%25e6%2594%25b6%25e5%2592%2597%25e6%259f%25af%25e6%2589%2593%25e5%25b9%25ab%25e6%25b2%2588%25e6%2597%25ad%25e6%259a%2589%25e6%2590%259c%25e9%259b%2586%25e6%2583%2585%25e5%25a0%25b1%25ef%25bc%259f&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoGt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=6eac5e4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://martinoei.com/article/27056/%e6%9e%97%e8%bc%9d-%e6%94%b6%e5%92%97%e6%9f%af%e6%89%93%e5%b9%ab%e6%b2%88%e6%97%ad%e6%9a%89%e6%90%9c%e9%9b%86%e6%83%85%e5%a0%b1%ef%bc%9f</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">佢係Roundtable既人，即係共諜mk輝既人</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">佢係Roundtable既人，即係共諜mk輝既人</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">佢係Roundtable既人，即係共諜mk輝既人</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n（LAM Fai Fred，1979年11月20日－），旅行家、專欄作家、智庫組織Roundtable Community前總幹事[1]、香港社會運動人士、註冊社工[2]。林於嶺南大學取得社會科學學士，後於中文大學取得社會工作碩士及註冊社工資格。[3]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/林輝\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E6%9E%97%E8%BC%9D&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoGt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=3f2c2191\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/林輝</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而琴日，有人開post講咁上下野，收各位聯絡資料</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【尋人】各個團體、中學聯署發起人請入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1176966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1176966</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n咪撚中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa5b7a3de4c76f28ab10d552169bf39bd409c7f","tid":1179143,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:36:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aadc76f6d084566a264c9a425824f1202c9a9262","tid":1179143,"uid":157074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"秋後算帳？"},{"pid":"427631691f3b76e1f5edc23ad2b671483061328a","tid":1179143,"uid":192068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T05:06:18.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b39ddd462d9963af8f1c0edc2c57e13d70261d3f","tid":1179143,"uid":31837,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"aadc76f6d084566a264c9a425824f1202c9a9262","tid":1179143,"uid":157074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"秋後算帳？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T05:08:48.000Z","msg":"搞小組討論扮凝聚力量，中央集權，解住解散"},{"pid":"dab3a29c9672f6266de2f329ce9a96f54fb23beb","tid":1179143,"uid":74058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T05:10:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 